-- Rainbow Tourism of Zimbabwe Full-Year Loss Narrowed
-- B y   B r i a n   L a t h a m
-- 2012-03-15T12:09:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-15/rainbow-tourism-of-zimbabwe-full-year-loss-narrowed-correct-.html
(Corrects earnings in first paragraph.)  Rainbow Tourism Group (RTG)  Ltd., a
Zimbabwean hospitality and leisure group, said its loss after
tax narrowed 68 percent to $389,475 for the year through
December.  Revenue increased to $27.3 million from $20.7 million a
year earlier, the Harare-based company said in an e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brian Latham in Johannesburg at 
